\id 1CO - Biblica® Open New Luo Translation 2020
\h 1 Jo-Korintho
\toc1 Jo-Korintho Mokwongo
\toc2 1 Jo-Korintho
\toc3 1Kor
\mt1 1 Jo-Korintho
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 An Paulo, moluongi mondo obed jaote mar Kristo Yesu kaluwore gi dwaro mar Nyasaye kaachiel kod owadwa Sostheno,
\b
\p 
\v 2 Wandikonu un kanisa mar Nyasaye man Korintho, ma un joma osepwodhi ei Kristo Yesu, kendo moseluongi mondo obed jomaler kaachiel gi ji mamoko duto man kamoro amora maluongo nying Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo, ma en Ruodhgi kendo Ruodhwa:
\b
\p 
\v 3 Ngʼwono gi kwe moa kuom Nyasaye Wuonwa kod Ruoth Yesu Kristo obed kodu.
\b
\s1 Dwoko erokamano
\p 
\v 4 Adwokone Nyasacha erokamano kinde duto kuomu, nikech ngʼwonone mosemiyou kuom Kristo Yesu.
\v 5 Nimar kuome usebedo momew e yore duto kuom weche ma uwacho kod ngʼeyo ma un-go,
\v 6 nikech nendwa kuom Kristo nosir e dieru.
\v 7 Kuom mano, ok uremo mich moro amora mar Roho kuritogo odiechiengʼ ma Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo nofwenyree.
\v 8 En bende obiro ritou mondo ubed motegno nyaka giko, mondo omi ubed maonge bura chiengʼ mar Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo.
\v 9 Nyasaye moseluongou mondo ubedi e lalruok gi Wuode Yesu Kristo Ruodhwa en ja-adiera.
\s1 Pogruok ei kanyakla mar joma oyie
\p 
\v 10 Jowetena, asayou e nying Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo, mondo un duto uwinjru ngʼato gi ngʼato. Kik pogruok moro amora bedi e kindu, to beduru kuriworu maonge pogruok, ka un gi dwaro achiel kod paro achiel.
\v 11 Jowetena, jood Kloe moko osekelona wach ni nitie dhawo e dieru.
\v 12 Tiend gima awacho chal kama: Ngʼat moro kuomu wacho niya, “An ngʼat Paulo,” to ngʼat machielo to wacho niya, “An ngʼat Apolo,” machielo bende oramo niya, “An ngʼat Kefa,” to moro wacho niya, “An ngʼat Kristo.”
\p 
\v 13 Kristo dipogre nyadi di? Paulo bende nogur e msalaba nikech un? Koso nuyudo batiso e nying Paulo?
\v 14 Adwoko erokamano ne Nyasaye ni ne ok abatiso ngʼato kuomu kata achiel makmana Krispo gi Gayo,
\v 15 omiyo onge ngʼama nyalo wacho ni noyudo batiso e nyinga.
\v 16 (Ee, jood Stefano bende ne abatiso, to ok apar ni ne abatiso ngʼat machielo mokalo mano.)
\v 17 Nikech Kristo ne ok oora mondo abatis ji, to noora mondo ayal Injili, ok gi weche mamit mag rieko dhano, nono to dipo ka msalap Kristo obedo tekone.
\s1 Kristo en rieko gi teko Nyasaye
\p 
\v 18 Wach msalaba en fuwo ni joma lal, to ni wan joma iwaro, en teko Nyasaye,
\v 19 nikech ondiki niya,
\q1 “Abiro ketho rieko joma riek;
\q2 kendo ngʼeyo mar joma riek abiro keyo nono.”\f + \fr 1:19 \ft \xt Isa 29:14\xt*\f*
\p 
\v 20 Ere ngʼama jarieko? Ere japuonj chik? Ere jatwak molony moloyo e pinyni? Donge Nyasaye osemiyo rieko mar pinyni odoko fuwo?
\v 21 Nyasaye nochano gi riekone ni piny ok nyal ngʼeyo Kristo gi riekone owuon, to nochano mana ni kuom fuwo mar wach mwalandoni ema owarogo joma oyie.
\v 22 Jo-Yahudi dwaro ni nyaka timnegi honni, to jo-Yunani to manyo rieko,
\v 23 to wan wayalo Kristo mane ogur, ma en kidi machwanyo jo-Yahudi kendo en fuwo ni joma ok jo-Yahudi.
\v 24 To kuom ji duto ma Nyasaye oseluongo, bed ni gin jo-Yahudi kata jo-Yunani, Kristo en teko Nyasaye kendo en rieko Nyasaye.
\v 25 Nikech fup Nyasaye riek moloyo rieko dhano, kendo nyawo mare otegno moloyo teko dhano.
\p 
\v 26 Jowetena, parieuru kaka nuchal kane Nyasaye oluongou. Ji mathoth kuomu ne ok joma riek, kipimou gi rieko dhano, bende ji mathoth kuomu ne ok joma rahuma kata joma oa e koth ruodhi.
\v 27 To Nyasaye noyiero gima ofuwo mag piny mondo okuodgo wi joma riek. Nyasaye noyiero bende gik manyap mag piny mondo okuodgo wi joma rateke.
\v 28 Nyasaye noyiero gik ma piny ochayo kendo manono mondo otiekgo gik ma jopiny kwano ni lich.
\v 29 Notimo kamano mondo kik ngʼato osungre e nyime.
\v 30 En e chakruok mar ngimau ei Kristo Yesu, mane obedonwa rieko moa kuom Nyasaye, tiende ni tim makare, pwodhruok, kod resruok.
\v 31 Emomiyo, mana kaka ondiki niya, “Ngʼat ma sungore mondo osungre kuom Jehova Nyasaye.”\f + \fr 1:31 \ft \xt Jer 9:24\xt*\f*
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Kuom mano jowetena, kane abiro iru to ne ok abiro gi weche mamit kata gi rieko kayalonu matut wach ma lingʼ-lingʼ mar Nyasaye.
\v 2 Nikech nangʼado wach e chunya ni kik angʼe gimoro amora machielo makmana Yesu Kristo kod gur mare.
\v 3 Ne abiro iru gi nyawo kod luoro, kendo ka denda duto tetni.
\v 4 Kane awuoyo kodu kendo ayalonu, to ne ok akonyora gi weche mamit kata mariek maywayo ji, to teko mar Roho ema onyisou ni wach mane ayalonu ne en adier
\v 5 mondo yieu kik gurre kuom rieko dhano, to ogurre mana kuom teko Nyasaye.
\s1 Rieko moa kuom Roho
\p 
\v 6 Kata kamano, wayalo rieko ni joma otegno, to ok rieko mag tiengʼni, kata mag ruodhi mandalogi, mabiro lal nono.
\v 7 Ooyo, wawuoyo kuom rieko mopondo mar Nyasaye, ma en rieko mosebedo kopandi kendo mane Nyasaye oikonwa nyaka aa chakruok piny mondo wayud duongʼ.
\v 8 Jotend pinyni kata achiel ok nowinjo tiend rieko mwayaloni, nikech ka dine giwinje, to ok dine giguro Ruodh Duongʼ.
\v 9 To en mana kaka ondiki niya,
\q1 “Onge wangʼ moseneno,
\q2 kata it mosewinjo,
\q1 kata paro mosengʼeyo
\q2 gima Nyasaye oseiko ne joma ohere.”\f + \fr 2:9 \ft \xt Isa 64:4\xt*\f*
\m 
\v 10 Wan to Nyasaye oseelonwa tiend wachne mopondo kuom teko mar Roho mare.
\p Roho Maler fwenyo gik moko duto, nyaka weche matut mag Nyasaye.
\v 11 Koso nitie ngʼato manyalo ngʼeyo pach ngʼat machielo? Donge chuny ngʼato owuon ema ongʼeyo gima ni e iye? Kamano bende e kaka onge ngʼat mongʼeyo pach Nyasaye makmana Roho mar Nyasaye.
\v 12 Roho mwaseyudo ok en roho mar piny, to en Roho moa kuom Nyasaye, mamiyo wangʼeyo mich ma Nyasaye osemiyowa.
\v 13 Mago e weche mwawuoyo kuomgi, ka ok wakonyre gi weche mopuonjwa gi rieko dhano, to wakonyore gi weche ma Roho ema opuonjo, kwalero adiera mag chuny gi weche mag chuny.
\v 14 To ngʼat ringruok ok nyal rwako gik moa kuom Roho mar Nyasaye, nikech onenogi kaka fuwo kendo ok onyal winjo tiendgi, nikech iwinjogi kuom Roho.
\v 15 Ngʼat man-gi Roho nono gik moko duto, to en to onge ngʼama none.
\q1 
\v 16 “Koso en ngʼa mosengʼeyo pach Jehova Nyasaye
\q2 ma dingʼadne rieko?”\f + \fr 2:16 \ft \xt Isa 40:13\xt*\f*
\m Wan to wan gi pach Kristo.
\c 3
\s1 Wach kuom pogruok e kanyakla mar joma oyie
\p 
\v 1 Jowetena, ne ok anyal wuoyo kodu kaka joma nigi Roho, to mana kaka jopiny ma pod mana nyithindo mayom kuom Kristo.
\v 2 Ne apidhou gi chak, to ok gi chiemo motegno nikech ne pok ubedo moikore ni chamo chiemo motegno. Kata sani pok uikorune.
\v 3 Donge pod un mana jopiny ka nyiego kod dhawo ni e kindu? Donge mano nyiso ni un jopiny kendo utimo timbe machalre gi timbe mag dhano?
\v 4 Nikech ka ngʼato wacho niya, “An ngʼat Paulo,” to ngʼat machielo to oramo niya, “An ngʼat Apolo,” to donge koro un ji ajia?
\p 
\v 5 Uparo ni Apolo to en ngʼa? Koso Paulo to en ngʼa? Gin mana jotich manomiyo uyie mana kaka Ruoth nomiyo ngʼato ka ngʼato tichne mondo otim.
\v 6 An ne achwoyo, to Apolo noolo pi, to Nyasaye ema nomiyo gidongo.
\v 7 Omiyo ngʼat mochwoyo kata ngʼat moolo pi ok en gimoro, makmana Nyasaye, mamiyo gik moko dongo.
\v 8 Jachwoyo gi jaol pi nigi thoro machalre, kendo ngʼato ka ngʼato kuomgi noyud pokne kaluwore gi tichne.
\v 9 Nikech waduto wan jotich kaachiel kod Nyasaye; un to un puoth Nyasaye kendo ot ma Nyasaye gero.
\p 
\v 10 Kuom ngʼwono ma Nyasaye osemiya, ne aketo mise kaka jagedo molony, kendo koro ngʼat machielo ema gedo e miseno. To ngʼato ka ngʼato nyaka ged kotangʼ.
\v 11 Nikech onge ngʼama nyalo keto mise machielo mopogore gi mano moseketi, ma en Yesu Kristo.
\v 12 Ka ngʼato ogedo e miseni kotiyo gi dhahabu kata gi fedha kata gi kite ma nengogi tek; kata gi bao, kata gi lum, kata gi saka,
\v 13 to tich jagedo ka jagedo nonenre kaka chal, nikech tich ngʼato nongʼere malongʼo Chiengʼ Ngʼado Bura. Chiengʼno, nofweny tich mar ngʼato ka ngʼato gi mach, nikech mach ema notemgo tich mane ngʼato ka ngʼato otiyo.
\v 14 Ka gima ne ngʼato ogero notony ma ok owangʼ e mach, to noyud michne.
\v 15 To ka tich ngʼato owangʼ e mach, to ok noyud michne. En owuon to norese, to norese mana ka ngʼat matony aa e mach maliel.
\p 
\v 16 Donge ungʼeyo ni un uwegi un e hekalu mar Nyasaye, kendo ni Roho mar Nyasaye odak eiu?
\v 17 Ka ngʼato oketho hekalu mar Nyasaye, to Nyasaye biro tieke, nikech hekalu mar Nyasaye ler, to un e hekaluno.
\p 
\v 18 Kik uwuondru. Ka ngʼato kuomu paro ni oriek e tiengʼni gi rieko mar pinyni, to onego olokre ngʼama ofuwo eka odok mariek.
\v 19 Nikech rieko mar pinyni en fuwo e nyim Nyasaye kaka ondiki niya, “Omako joma riek gi riekogi giwegi”\f + \fr 3:19 \ft \xt Ayu 5:13\xt*\f*;
\v 20 kendo mana kaka ondiki niya, “Jehova Nyasaye ongʼeyo pach joma riek ni onge tich.”\f + \fr 3:20 \ft \xt Zab 94:11\xt*\f*
\v 21 Kuom mano, kik ngʼato sungre kuom dhano! Gik moko duto gin mau.
\v 22 Bed ni en Paulo kata Apolo, kata Kefa, kata piny, kata ngima, kata tho, kata gik ndalogi, kata gik mantiere, kata gik moko mabiro giduto gin mau.
\v 23 Un to un mag Kristo, to Kristo en mar Nyasaye.
\c 4
\s1 Joote mag Kristo
\p 
\v 1 Kuom mano, ji onego okwanwa kaka jotich Kristo, kendo kaka jorit weche mopondo mag Nyasaye.
\v 2 To ongʼere ni joma omi tich mar rito nyaka bed jo-adiera.
\v 3 An awuon ok lichna ka uyala kata ka oyala e od bura moro amora mar dhano. Chutho kata an awuon ok anyal yalora kenda.
\v 4 Chutho ok ane gimoro ma aketho, to mano ok onyisa ni aonge ketho. To Ruoth ema ngʼadona bura.
\v 5 Kuom mano kik ungʼad bura kapok kinde ochopo, to rituru biro mar Ruoth. En owuon noel e lela gik masani opondo e mudho, kendo enonyis paro duto mopondo e chuny dhano. E kindeno ema ngʼato ka ngʼato noyud pak moa kuom Nyasaye.
\p 
\v 6 Jowetena, koro asewuoyo kodu ka akonyora gi nyinga kod nying Apolo kaka ranyisi mondo uyud konyruok, kupuonjoru kuomwa tiend wach mawacho niya, “Kik ukal weche mondiki.” Mano biro miyo ok udhial ngʼato moloyo nyawadgi.
\v 7 Angʼo momiyo iparo ni iber moloyo ngʼat machielo? Angʼo ma in-go mane ok omiyi? To ka gima in-gono nomiyi, to angʼo momiyo isungori mana ka gima ne ok omiyigo?
\p 
\v 8 Un ero un gi gik moko duto mudwaro kendo usedoko jo-mwandu! Usebedo ruodhi, to wan uwewa oko! Mano kaka agombo ni ne ubed ruodhi adier mondo wan bende wabed ruodhi kaachiel kodu!
\v 9 Nikech nenorena ni Nyasaye oseketowa wan joote, ka joma odongʼ chien bangʼ ji, kendo mana ka joma osengʼadnegi buch tho mondo onegi e dier pap. Oseketwa wabedo joma piny duto rango kendo malaike kod ji bende rangowa.
\v 10 Wan wafuwo nikech Kristo, to un to uriek ei Kristo! Wan wanyap, to un to uroteke! Un imiyou duongʼ, to wan to ochawa!
\v 11 Nyaka koroni kech kayowa kendo riyo oloyowa. Warwako lewni mokidhore okidhore, kendo isandowa malit, ka waonge kata kar dak.
\v 12 Watiyo matek gi lwetewa. Ka ikwongʼowa, to wagwedho joma kwongʼowa; kisandowa, to wayie isandowa asanda;
\v 13 bende ka iyanyowa, to wadwoko gi weche mangʼwon. Nyaka koroni wasedoko machal gi yugi mag piny; wachalo gik mowit oko ni onge tich!
\p 
\v 14 Ok andiknu wechegi mondo akuodgo wiu, to andikonugi mondo ajiwu, kaka nyithinda mageno.
\v 15 Kata obedo ni un gi ji alufu apar ma ritou e Kristo, to uonge gi wuone mangʼeny, nikech kuom Kristo Yesu, an ema ne abedo kaka wuonu kane ayalonu Injili.
\v 16 Kuom mano, akwayou mondo ulu timna.
\v 17 Mano emomiyo aoronu Timotheo, ma en wuoda mahero, kendo ma ja-adiera kuom Ruoth. Obiro paronu kit ngimana kuom Kristo Yesu, ma ok opogore gi gik mapuonjo kuonde duto, e kanisa.
\p 
\v 18 Jomoko kuomu sunga omako, mana ka gima ok abi biro iru.
\v 19 To abiro biro mapiyo ka Ruoth Nyasaye oyie, kendo kabiro, to anadwar ngʼeyo ok mana kaka josungago wuoyo kende, to bende napenjgi teko ma gin-go.
\v 20 Nikech pinyruoth Nyasaye ok otenore mana kuom weche miwacho gidhok, to otenore kuom teko maduongʼ.
\v 21 Koro ere gima udwaro? Udwaro ni mondo abi iru katingʼo boka, koso abi gihera kod chuny mamuol?
\c 5
\s1 Siem kuom terruok
\p 
\v 1 Wachore e lela ni nitie terruok e dieru, kendo ni en kit terruok ma kata jopiny ok tim; nikech ngʼato terore gi chi wuon.
\v 2 To bende pod usungoru asunga! Donge onego bed ni upongʼ gi kuyo mondo ugol oko ngʼat matimo kamano e dieru?
\v 3 Kata obedo ni aonge kodu kuno e ringruok, to ngʼeuru ni an kodu kuom chuny. An to asengʼadone ngʼat matimo tim marachno bura, mana ka gima ne an kodu kuno.
\v 4 Ka uchokoru e nying Ruodhwa Yesu, kendo an kodu kuom chuny, kendo teko mar Ruodhwa Yesu bende ni kodu,
\v 5 to keturu ngʼatni e lwet Satan mondo ringre mohero richono okethi, to chunye to mondo oresi chiengʼ biro Ruoth.
\p 
\v 6 Sungau ok ber. Donge ungʼeyo ni thowi matin kende oromo kuodo mogo modwal duto?
\v 7 Goluru thowi machon-no oko e dieru mondo ubed maler chutho, eka unubed ka mogo modwal manyien ma ok oketie thowi, nimar kamano e kaka uchalo. Kristo, ma en nyarombowa mar Pasaka, osetimgo misango.
\v 8 Emomiyo koro watimuru sawo, ok gi thowi machon mar himruok kod timbe maricho, to watime gi makati ma ok oketie thowi, ma en makati mar wuotho e ler kod adiera.
\p 
\v 9 Ne asendikonu e barupa motelo ni kik ubedi e kanyakla mar joma terore.
\v 10 Ok awuo kuom jopiny mapok oyie ma terore, kata ma jowuoro, kata ma jomecho, kata malamo nyiseche manono, nikech mano to dichunwa ni wadar e pinyni.
\v 11 To koro andikonu mondo kik ubedi e kanyakla gi ngʼato angʼata maluongore ni owadu kuom Ruoth, to pod terore, kata ma jawuoro, kata malamo nyiseche manono, kata ma jaketh nying ji, kata ma jamer, kata ma jamecho. Ngʼat ma kamano kata chiemo kik uchiemgo.
\p 
\v 12 Donge ok en tichna mondo angʼad bura ne joma ok jo-Kristo? Donge joma osebedo e kanyakla mar joma oyie ema onego ungʼadnigi bura?
\v 13 Nyasaye biro ngʼado bura ni joma ni oko, omiyo riemburu jarichono oa e dieru.\f + \fr 5:13 \ft \xt Rap 17:7; 19:19; 21:21; 22:21,24; 24:7\xt*\f*
\c 6
\s1 Joma oyie kuom Kristo kik donj ne jowetegi e od bura
\p 
\v 1 Ka ngʼato moro kuomu nigi wach moro gi wadgi, ere kaka doter wachno e nyim joma okia Nyasaye mondo ongʼad bucheno, kar kelo wachno e nyim jomaler?
\v 2 Donge ungʼeyo ni jomaler ema biro ngʼadone piny bura? Ka un ema onego ungʼadne piny bura, to donge mano nyiso ni unyalo ngʼado bura kuom weche matindo man e kind ji?
\v 3 Donge ungʼeyo ni wan ema wabiro ngʼado bura ne malaike? Koro gige pinyni to donge wanyalo ngʼadone bura moloyo!
\v 4 Ka kamano, to angʼo momiyo ka un gi wach e dieru, to uyiero jongʼad bura ma jopiny ma kwan-gi onge ei kanisa.
\v 5 Awacho mano mondo akuodgo wiu. Bende dibed ni onge ngʼato e dieru kata achiel mariek manyalo ngʼado bura weche man e kind joma oyie?
\v 6 Kar timo kamano, to yudore ni ja-Kristo donjo ne ja-Kristo wadgi e od bura kendo utimo mano e buch jopiny!
\p 
\v 7 Kaka un gi buche e kindu kamano, nyiso ni un joma oserem chuth. Kar donjo ne wadu e buch jopiny, to ok iyie otimni atima marach? Ok iweye owuondi awuonda?
\v 8 Kar timo kamano, to un ema uwuondo joweteu kendo utimonegi marach, to eka utimo kamano mana ni joweteu kuom yie.
\p 
\v 9 Donge ungʼeyo ni joma timo timbe maricho ok noyud gweth mar pinyruoth Nyasaye? Kik ngʼato wuondu! Ngʼeuru ni jochode kata joma lamo nyiseche manono, kata joma terore, kata chwo ma terore gi chwo wetegi,
\v 10 kata jokuo, kata jowuoro, kata jomer, kata joketh nying ji, kata jomecho, ok noyud gweth mar pinyruoth Nyasaye.
\v 11 Kamano e kaka jomoko kuomu ne chalo. To ne olwoku mi opwodhu, mi oketu udoko joma kare e nying Ruoth Yesu Kristo, kendo kuom Roho mar Nyasachwa.
\s1 Richo mar terruok
\p 
\v 12 Ngʼato nyalo wacho niya, “Oyiena timo gimoro amora madwaro,” to gik moko duto ma watimo ok kelnwa konyruok. Bende ngʼato nyalo medo wacho niya, “Oyiena timo gimoro amora madwaro,” to ok anyal yie gimoro loka misumbane.
\v 13 “Chiemo en mar ich, ich en mar chiemo,” to Nyasaye biro ketho gik moko ariyo duto. Ringruok ok en mar terruok, to en mar miyo Ruoth duongʼ, mana kaka Ruoth bende en mar ringruok.
\v 14 Kuom teko Nyasaye nochiero Ruoth Yesu oa kuom joma otho kendo wan bende obiro chierowa.
\v 15 Donge ungʼeyo ni ringreu gin fuonde Kristo owuon? Bende dakaw fuonde Kristo mondo ariw gi dhako ma jachode? Mano ok nyal timore ngangʼ!
\v 16 Koso ukia ni ngʼat moriwore gi dhako ma jachode bedo kode e achiel kuom ringruok? Ndiko wacho niya, “Ji ariyogo nodok ringruok achiel.”\f + \fr 6:16 \ft \xt Chak 2:24\xt*\f*
\v 17 To ngʼat moriwore gi Ruoth doko chuny achiel kode.
\p 
\v 18 Ringuru utony ni terruok. Richo duto ma ngʼato timo otimo oko mar ringre, to ngʼat machodo timo richo ni ringre owuon.
\v 19 Donge ungʼeyo ni ringreu en hekalu mar Roho Maler modak eiu kendo ma Nyasaye osechiwonu? Ok un mau uwegi;
\v 20 to nongʼiewu gi nengo matek. Omiyo miuru Nyasaye duongʼ gi ringreu.
\c 7
\s1 Weche mag kend
\p 
\v 1 To koro kuom weche mane upenja e barupu, anyalo wacho ni ber mondo ngʼato kik okendi.
\v 2 To nikech weche mag terruok ngʼeny, ngʼato ka ngʼato nyaka bed gi chiege owuon kendo dhako ka dhako obed gi chwore owuon.
\v 3 Dichwo nyaka chop dwach chiege kaka joma okendore, kendo dhako bende nyaka tim kamano ni chwore.
\v 4 Nikech dhako mokendi onge gi teko kuom ringre owuon, to en mar chwore. Kamano bende, dichwo mokendo onge gi teko kuom ringre owuon, to en mar chiege bende.
\v 5 Kik utuonru makmana ka uwinjoru e kindu uwegi mar timo mano kuom kinde machwok mondo uchiwru ni lamo. To bangʼ chiwruok ni lamo, to uchak uriwru kendo mondo kik Satan temu, nikech ok unyal ritoru.
\v 6 Awachonu kamano koa e pacha awuon, to ok kaka chik dwaro.
\v 7 Dobedo maberna moloyo ka ji duto obedo kaka an, to kata kamano, ngʼato ka ngʼato nigi michne ma Nyasaye omiye, ngʼat moro nigi michni, to ngʼat machielo bende nigi mich machielo.
\p 
\v 8 To joma pok okendi gi joma pok okendo, kod mon ma chwogi otho, to awachonegi kama: En gima ber moloyo ka gisiko ma ok gikendo kata okendgi, mana kaka an.
\v 9 To ka ok ginyal ritore giwegi, to onego gikendi, kata okendgi nikech kend ber moloyo ka gombo wangʼo ngʼato ka mach.
\p 
\v 10 To ne joma osekendo gi joma osekendi achiwonegi chik (chutho ok an, to Ruoth) kama: Dhako kik were gi chwore.
\v 11 To kapo ni otimo kamano, to ochune ni nyaka osik maonge dichwo, to ka ok kamano to odog ir chwore, kendo dichwo bende kik riemb chiege.
\p 
\v 12 To kuom ji mamoko modongʼ (chutho ok Ruoth, to an ema awachonegi) kama: Ka owadwa moro ma ja-Kristo nigi dhako ma ok oyie, kendo dhakono oyie dak kode, to kik oriembe.
\v 13 Bende ka dhako nigi dichwo ma ok oyie, to dichwono oyie dak kode kaka chiege, to kik oweye.
\v 14 Nikech dichwo mapok oyie inyalo pwodho nikech chiege, to dhako mapok oyie bende inyalo pwodho nikech chwore moyie. Ka ok kamano, to nyithindu dibed mogak, to koro sani to ginenore ni giler.
\p 
\v 15 To ka ngʼat ma ok oyie ojok noa, to weye aweya odhi. Dichwo moyie kata dhako moyie ok otwe e weche ma kamago, nikech Nyasaye oseluongowa mondo wadag gi kwe.
\v 16 Ingʼeyo nadi, in dhako, kata inyalo miyo chwori yudo warruok? Koso, ingʼeyo nade, in dichwo, ni chiegi nyalo yudo warruok nikech in?
\p 
\v 17 Kata kamano, ngʼato ka ngʼato onego odag ngimano mane Ruoth oluonge kendo owuoth wuodhno mane Nyasaye oluongee. Ma e chik ma aseketo ne kanisa.
\v 18 Dibed ni ngʼato noluongi koseter nyangu? Kik ogomb ni ne ok otere nyangu. Dibed ni ngʼato noluongi kapok oter nyangu? Ngʼat ma kamano kik ter nyangu.
\v 19 Bedo ni ngʼato oter nyangu kata ok oter nyangu ok en gimoro. Gima duongʼ en rito Chike Nyasaye.
\v 20 Omiyo ngʼato ka ngʼato mondo obed mana kaka ne en kane Nyasaye oluonge.
\v 21 Dibed ni ne in misumba kane Nyasaye oluongi? Kik mano chandi, makmana kapo ni inyalo yudo yor bedo thuolo, to tim kamano moloyo.
\v 22 Nikech ngʼat mane Ruoth oluongo ka misumba koro bedo ngʼat man thuolo kuom Ruoth, to bende ngʼat mane ni thuolo kane Ruoth oluongo doko misumba Kristo.
\v 23 Nongʼiewu gi nengo matek, omiyo kik ubed wasumbini mag ji.
\v 24 Jowetena, ngʼato ka ngʼato nigi tingʼ e nyim Nyasaye mondo osik mana kaka Nyasaye noluongeno.
\p 
\v 25 Kuom wach nyiri ma ok okendi to awacho kama: Aonge gi chik moa kuom Ruoth, to achiwo pacha kaka ngʼat ma wechene inyalo geno kuom ngʼwono mar Ruoth.
\v 26 Nikech chandruok mantie sani, aparo ni ber mondo usik kaka uchal.
\v 27 Dibed ni ngʼato osekendi? Ka kamano, to kik idwar mondo iweri gi chwori. Dibed ni pok ikendo? Kichal kamano, to kik imany nyako mondo ikendi.
\v 28 To ka ikendo, to ok itimo richo; kata ka nyako okendi bende ok otimo richo. To joma okendo gi mokendi biro neno chandruok mathoth e ngimani, to adwaro ni akonyu mondo kik une chandruokni.
\p 
\v 29 Jowetena, gima awachonu en ni sa odongʼ matin. Chakre sani koro joma nigi mon onego odag ka gima giongego;
\v 30 joma ywak onego bedi ka joma ok ywagi; joma mor onego odag ka joma ok nigi mor; joma ngʼiewo gimoro onego odag ka gima gik ma gingʼiewogo ok mag-gi,
\v 31 joma konyore gi gige piny bende kik yie chunygi gedi e gigo, nikech piny ma waneno sani-ni biro kadho.
\p 
\v 32 Adwaro ni mondo ubed maonge gi kit parruok moro amora. Dichwo ma ok okendo, weche Ruoth ema omako, kaka onyalo siko kotimo gik mamoro Ruoth,
\v 33 to ngʼama osekendo, to pache omoko e weche pinyni, kaka onyalo timo gik mamiyo chiege mor.
\v 34 Kendo dwarone bende opogore nyadiriyo. Dhako ma ok okendi, kata nyako ngili, paro kuom weche Ruoth. Thorogi maduongʼ en mondo gibed maler e ringregi gi chunygi. To dhako mokendi, to pache ni kuom gige piny, kaka onyalo miyo chwore mor.
\v 35 Awacho wechegi mondo uyud konyruok kuomgi, to ok mondo aketnu chik manyaka uluw. Adwaro ni udagi e yo maber, ka chiwruoku ni Ruoth ok opogore.
\p 
\v 36 Ka ngʼato paro ni ok otim maber ne osiepne ma nyako mangili modwaro nyuomo, kendo ka nyakono hike koro medore, to dichwono oneno ni onego okende, to ber mondo okend nyakono. Oonge gi ketho kotimo kamano kendo onego gikendre.
\v 37 To dichwo mosengʼado wach e pache owuon, kendo manyalo chiko dwache maonge ngʼama ochune, koseneno e chunye ni ok odwar nyuomo nyakono, en bende otimo maber.
\v 38 Kuom mano, ngʼat monyuomo nyako mangilino otimo maber, to ngʼat ma ok onywome otimo maber moloyo.
\p 
\v 39 Chik otweyo dhako gi chwore ndalo duto ma chwore ngima. To ka chwore otho, to en thuolo mondo onywome gi dichwo moro amora mohero, makmana ni nyaka nyuome gi ngʼat kuom Ruoth.
\v 40 An to pacha neno ni dhako ma chwore otho nyalo neno maber moloyo ka ok ochak onywome, kendo awacho mano ka aparo ni an-gi Roho mar Nyasaye.
\c 8
\s1 Chiemo motimgo misango ne nyiseche manono
\p 
\v 1 Kuom wach chiemo motimgo misango ni nyiseche manono to awachoe kama: Wangʼeyo ni wan duto wan gi rieko. Rieko kelo sunga ni dhano, to hera to gero ji.
\v 2 Ngʼat makawore ni ongʼeyo gimoro kik par ni osengʼeyo moromo kaka dwarore.
\v 3 To ngʼat mohero Nyasaye, to Nyasaye ongʼeyo.
\p 
\v 4 To kuom wach mar chamo chiemo motimgo misango ni nyiseche manono, to awachoe kama: Wangʼeyo ni “Nyasaye manono en gima nono e piny-ka,” kendo wangʼeyo ni “Onge Nyasaye moro makmana achiel.”
\v 5 Nikech kata bed ni gik miluongo ni nyisechego nitie, kata gibed e polo, kata e piny mana (kaka nitie “nyiseche” mangʼeny kod “ruodhi” mangʼeny),
\v 6 wan to wangʼeyo ni nitie Nyasaye achiel kende, ma en Wuoro. En ema gik moko duto noa kuome, kendo nomiyowa ngima. Bende nitie Ruoth achiel kende ma en Yesu Kristo. En ema nomiyo gik moko duto obetie kendo en ema omiyowa ngima.
\p 
\v 7 To ji duto ok ongʼeyo wachni. Jomoko pod ongʼiyo gi nyiseche manono ma ka gichamo chiemo makamano to giparo mana ni en motimnigo nyasaye manono misango; to nikech chunygi mar pogo ber gi rach otho, gidoko mochido.
\v 8 To chiemo ok kelwa machiegni gi Nyasaye. Kata ka ok wachiemo, to ok wabed jomaricho, to bende ka wachiemo, to onge ohala ma wayudo.
\p 
\v 9 Kuom mano, bed motangʼ mondo thuolo ma in-go mar chiemo kata mar weyo chiemo kik lokre kidi mar chwanyruok ni joma yiegi yomyom.
\v 10 Nikech ka ngʼat man-gi yie mayomyomno oneni, in miwacho ni in gi yie motegno, kichiemo e hekalu mar nyiseche manono, donge mano nyalo ywaye mi ocham chiemo motimgo misango ni nyiseche manono?
\v 11 Omiyo ngʼat man-gi yie mayomyomni ma Kristo nothoneno koro kethore mana nikech rieko miwachogo ni iriek.
\v 12 Sa ma itimo richo ni joweteni e yo makamano, kihinyo chunygi mayom yom, ngʼeni itimo richo ni Kristo.
\v 13 Kuom mano, ka gima achamo nyalo miyo wadwa donjo e richo, to abiro weyo chamo ringʼo chuth mondo kik ami opodhi.
\c 9
\s1 Ratiro mag jaote
\p 
\v 1 To donge an thuolo? Donge an jaote? Donge ne aneno Yesu Ruodhwa? Koso donge un olemo mar tichna kuom Ruoth?
\v 2 Kata ka jomoko ok okawa kaka jaote, to un owinjore ukawa kamano, nikech un e ranyisi mar bedona jaote kuom Ruoth.
\p 
\v 3 Joma ngʼadona bura to adwoko kama.
\v 4 Donge wan gi ratiro mondo omiwa chiemo gi math?
\v 5 Donge wan gi ratiro mar wuotho gi mondewa e wuodhewa mag Injili kaka joote mamoko, kendo kaka jowete Ruoth kod Petro johero timo?
\v 6 Koso an kod Barnaba ema nyaka wati eka wachiem?
\p 
\v 7 En jalweny mane machulo pokne kende ka en e lweny? En japur mane ma ok cham olemo mowuok e puothe mar mzabibu? Koso jakwath mane makwayo jamni, to ok omadhi cha jamnigo?
\v 8 Koso awuoyo awuoya ka dhano? Donge Chik bende jiwo wachni?
\v 9 Nimar ondiki e chik Musa niya, “Kik utwe dho dhiangʼ kaywayo lodi ma idinogo cham.”\f + \fr 9:9 \ft \xt Rap 25:4\xt*\f* Uparo ni wach rwedhi ema ne chando chuny Nyasaye koso?
\v 10 Donge wan ema ne owuoyo kuomwa kowacho wachni? Ee, wachni ne ondiknwa, nikech ka japur puro kendo jakeyo keyo, to gitimo kamano ka gigeno ni ibiro pognigi cham moko.
\v 11 Ka wachwoyo kodhi mar chuny e dieru, to ere rachne ka wakayo kuomu gik mwakonyorego?
\v 12 Ka joma moko to nigi ratironi mar yudo konyruokgi koa kuomu, donge wan onego wabed gi ratiro makamano moloyogi?
\p Wan to pok wakonyore gi ratironi. Kar timo kamano, to wasetuonore yuto mawa mondo kik waket obadho moro amora manyalo gengʼo Injili mar Kristo.
\v 13 Donge ungʼeyo ni joma tiyo e hekalu yudo chiembgi koa e hekalu, kendo ni joma chiwo misango ewi kendo mar misango ipogonegi misangogo?
\v 14 Kamano bende e kaka Ruoth Nyasaye nochiko mondo joma lando Injili oyud konyruok duto mag ngimagi koa kuom Injili ma giyalo.
\p 
\v 15 An to pok akonyora gi ratiro mawan-gogi kata achiel, kendo kata sani ok andiknu wechegi mondo akwau kony monego ayudi koa kuomu. Dine obedo maberna ka atho moloyo ka ayiene ngʼato oketho sunganani.
\v 16 Kata kamano, ka ayalo Injili, to ok onego asungra, nikech ochuna ni nyaka ayal. Mano kaka dibed malitna ka ok ayalo Injili!
\v 17 Ka ayalo kuom dwarona to ayudo mich, to ka ok kuom dwarona, to mano nyiso ni achopo ote mano mane omiya.
\v 18 To kara michna en angʼo? En ni mondo ayal Injili maonge gima ochula, mondo kik akonyra gi ratiro ma an-go e tich mar lando Injili.
\p 
\v 19 Nikech kata obedo ni an thuolo kendo ok an misumba ngʼato, to aselokora misumba ji duto mondo alok ji mangʼeny oyie kuom Kristo.
\v 20 Ka atiyo e dier jo-Yahudi, to adoko machal kodgi mondo alokgi. Ka atiyo e dier joma luwo chik, to achalo ngʼama luwo chik (kata obedo ni an awuon ok an e bwo chik), eka alok joma luwo chik.
\v 21 Ka atiyo e dier joma onge chik, ne adoko machal kodgi (kata obedo ni chik Nyasaye ok oweya oko nikech an e bwo chik Kristo), eka alok joma onge chik.
\v 22 Joma nyap ne abedonegi manyap eka alokgi. Asetimora gimoro amora ni ji duto mondo atem reso moko kuomgi e yo moro amora manyalore.
\v 23 Magi duto atimo nikech wach Injili, mondo an bende ayud gweth kuom Injilino.
\p 
\v 24 Donge ungʼeyo ni e piem mar ngʼwech jongʼwech, duto ringo, to ngʼato achiel kende ema yudo mich? Omiyo ringuru e yo madimi uyud mich.
\v 25 Jangʼwech ka jangʼwech madhi e piem ritore e yore duto. Gitimo kamano mondo giyud osimbo ma ok siki; wan to waritore mondo wayud osimbo mabiro siko nyaka chiengʼ.
\v 26 Emomiyo an ok aringi ka ngʼama okia kuma itieke ngʼwech, bende ok athor diro ngum adira ka gima agoyo yamo nono.
\v 27 Ooyo, asando ringra mondo owinj wachna, mondo kik yud ni an awuon ok ayudo osimb loch, bangʼ yalo Injili ne ji mamoko.
\c 10
\s1 Siem miyudo kuom sigand Israel
\p 
\v 1 Jowetena, ok adwar ni mondo ukia kaka kwerewa nowuotho e bwo bor polo, to kendo giduto negingʼado Nam Makwar.
\v 2 Bedo e bwo bor polono kendo ngʼado nam makwarno ema nokwan ka batiso mane omiyo gibetie achiel gi Musa.
\v 3 Giduto negichamo chiemb chuny machalre
\v 4 kendo giduto ne gimodho pi achiel mar chuny, nikech ne gimodho e lwanda mar chuny mane wuotho kodgi; to lwandano ne en Kristo.
\v 5 To kata kamano, Nyasaye ne ok omor gi ji mangʼeny kuomgi, kendo ringregi nodongʼ e thim.
\p 
\v 6 Gigi duto notimore mondo obednwa ranyisi masiemowa mondo kik wagomb gik maricho kaka ne gigombo.
\v 7 Kik ulam nyiseche manono kaka moko kuomgi nolamo, mana kaka ondiki niya, “Ji nobet piny mondo gichiem kendo gimethi, kendo negia malo mondo gimiel miende dwanyruok mag oganda.”\f + \fr 10:7 \ft \xt Wuo 32:6\xt*\f*
\v 8 Kik waterre kaka moko kuomgi notimo, mi ji alufu piero ariyo gadek kuomgi notho odiechiengʼ achiel.
\v 9 Kik watem Ruoth, kaka moko kuomgi notimo, mi thuonde nonegogi.
\v 10 Bende kik wangʼur, kaka moko kuomgi notimo, mi malaika mar tho nonegogi.
\p 
\v 11 Gigi duto notimorenigi kaka ranyisi, kendo nondiknwagi mondo gibednwa siem, wan ma wadak e ndalo ma giko piny chiegnini.
\v 12 Omiyo, ka iparo ni ichungʼ motegno bed motangʼ, nono to ipodho!
\v 13 Onge tem museneno mopogore gi ma ji duto neno. Nyasaye rito singruokne, ok obi yie mondo otemu mohingo tekreu. To e sa ma itemoueno, obiro miyou yo munyalo tonygo mondo ubed gi teko mar timo sinani.
\s1 Nyasi mag nyiseche manono kod Sawo mar Ruoth
\p 
\v 14 Kuom mano, osiepena mageno, ringuru ua kuom nyiseche manono.
\v 15 Awuoyo kodu kaka joma parogi nikare, omiyo paruru matut tiend wach ma awachonuno.
\v 16 Donge kikombe mar gweth ma wagoyene Nyasaye erokamano ketowa e lalruok achiel e remb Kristo? Koso makati mwangʼingo donge ketowa e lalruok achiel, e ringre Kristo?
\v 17 Nikech nitie makati achiel, koro wan ringruok achiel, kata obedo ni wangʼeny, nikech wan duto wachamo makati achielno.
\p 
\v 18 Ka wakawo jo-Israel kaka ranyisi: Donge joma chamo gik mokete kendo mar misango bet e lalruok achiel gi kendo mar misangono?
\v 19 Diponi awacho ni misango mochiwne nyiseche manono en gimoro kata ni nyasaye manono nigi tiende?
\v 20 Ooyo! Awacho ni misango ma jopiny makia Nyasaye timo, gitimo ni jochiende, to ok ni Nyasaye. To ok adwar mondo ubedi e lalruok achiel gi jochiende.
\v 21 Ok unyal madho kikombe Ruoth kaachiel gi kikombe jochiende bende; kendo ok unyal chiemo e mesa Ruoth, ka uchiemo e mesa jochiende bende.
\v 22 Koso wadwaro miyo Ruoth mirima? Waparo ni watek moloye?
\s1 Thuolo mar joma oyie kuom Kristo
\p 
\v 23 Ngʼato nyalo wacho niya, “Oyiena timo gimoro amora mwadwaro,” to gik moko duto ma watimo ok kelnwa konyruok. Ngʼat machielo to wacho niya, “Oyiena timo gimoro amora madwaro,” to gik moko duto ma watimo ok kelnwa dongruok.
\v 24 Kik ngʼato dwar mana gik makonye en owuon, to ngʼato mondo odwar gima konyo jowadgi bende.
\p 
\v 25 Un thuolo mar chamo ringʼo mongʼiew e chiro ma ok ubedo gi penjo mathoth e chunyu
\v 26 nikech Muma wacho niya, “Piny kaachiel gi gik moko duto manie iye, gin mag Jehova Nyasaye.”\f + \fr 10:26 \ft \xt Zab 24:1\xt*\f*
\p 
\v 27 Ka ngʼat ma ok oyie kuom Kristo ogweli e chiemo, kendo ihero dhi, to cham gimoro amora moketi e nyimi ma ok ichich gi penjo mathoth e chunyi.
\v 28 To ka ngʼato onyisi niya, “Chiemoni ne olosi mondo otimgo misango ne nyiseche manono,” to kik icham chiemono, nikech wach ma ngʼatno onyisino, kendo nikech wach mar chich ma in-go.
\v 29 Tim kamano mar konyo chuny ngʼatno, to ok nikech konyruokni. Ere gima omiyo paro manie chuny ngʼat machielo ema mona timo gima aneno ni an gi thuolo mar timo?
\v 30 Ka agoyo erokamano ni chiemo ma achamo, to angʼo momiyo ikwana ka jaketho ne gima agoyonee Nyasaye erokamano?
\p 
\v 31 Omiyo gimoro amora mutimo, bed ni uchiemo kata umetho, to timgiuru duto mondo Nyasaye oyud duongʼ.
\v 32 Kik ubed rachwany ni jo-Yahudi, kata ni jo-Yunani, kata ni kanisa Nyasaye,
\v 33 mana kaka an awuon atemo moro ji duto e gik moko duto matimo, ka ok amany mana gik makonya an awuon, to atimo gik makonyo ji mangʼeny, mondo kanyalore to giyud warruok.
\c 11
\nb 
\v 1 Luwuru timna, mana kaka an bende aluwo tim Kristo.
\s1 Gik madwarore e lemo
\p 
\v 2 Agoyonu erokamano nikech usiko upara e yore duto, kendo nikech umako puonj duto mane amiyou.
\v 3 To adwaro mondo ungʼe ni Kristo ewi dichwo ka dichwo, kendo ni dichwo ewi dhako, to Nyasaye ewi Kristo.
\v 4 Kuom mano, dichwo malemo kata makoro e chokruok koumo wiye ochayo Kristo.
\v 5 Kamano bende dhako malemo kata makoro e chokruok, ka ok otweyo kitamba okuodo wi chwore, nikech onge pogruok e kinde gi dhako moliel yie wiye.
\v 6 Ka dhako ok dwar tweyo kitamba, to ber kata mondo oliel yie wiye. To kaka en wichkuot ka dhako olielo yie wiye mapoth, to ber otwe kitamba.
\p 
\v 7 Dichwo to ok owinjore oum wiye nikech en ranyisi mar Nyasaye gi duongʼne; dhako to en ranyisi mar duongʼ mar dichwo.
\v 8 Dichwo ne ok oa kuom dhako, to dhako ema ne oa kuom dichwo.
\v 9 To bende, dichwo ne ok ochwe ne dhako, to dhako ema ne ochwe ni dichwo.
\v 10 Nikech wachni kendo nikech malaike, dhako mondo oum wiye kaka ranyisi ni en e bwo loch.
\v 11 Kata kamano, kuom Ruoth, dhako ok nyal dak maonge dichwo mana kaka dichwo bende ok nyal dak maonge dhako.
\v 12 Nimar, mana kaka dhako nochwe koa kuom dichwo, e kaka dichwo bende inywolo gi dhako, to gik moko duto oa kuom Nyasaye.
\p 
\v 13 Penjreuru un uwegi ni: Bende en gima kare mondo dhako olam Nyasaye ka ok otweyo kitamba e wiye?
\v 14 Donge en gima ongʼere ne ji duto ni wich maboyo en wichkuot ni dichwo?
\v 15 To ka dhako yie wiye boyo, to en duongʼ mare, nikech yie wich maboyo omiye kaka raum.
\v 16 Ka ngʼato kuomu dwaro kwedo ma, to ongʼe ni waonge gi tim mopogore gi mwapuonjoni, kendo kata kanise duto mag Nyasaye ongego.
\s1 Sawo mar Ruoth
\p 
\v 17 Puonj makoro amiyou sani to ok anyal pakoue, nikech kinde duto ma uchokoru kaachiel to chokruoku kelo mana rach kar kelo ber.
\v 18 Mokwongo awinjo ni ka uchokoru kaachiel kaka kanisa, to nitie pogruok e kindu, kendo anyalo yie ni wachno en adier.
\v 19 Mano emomiyo nitiere pogruok e kindu mondo joma Nyasaye oyiego ongʼere maler.
\v 20 Ka uchokoru kanyakla, to nenore ni ok ucham Sap Ruoth;
\v 21 nikech ka uchiemo to ngʼato ka ngʼato rikni gichamo chiembe owuon, ma ok orito jowetene; omiyo jomoko kuomu denyo, to jomoko kuomu to mer.
\v 22 Donge un gi miechu munyalo chiemoe kendo methoe? Koso uchayo kanisa Nyasaye, momiyo ukuodo wi joma ochando? Angʼo ma dawachnu? Uparo ni dapaku kuom wachni? Ok kamano ngangʼ!
\p 
\v 23 Puonj mane ayudo kuom Ruoth mi amiyou chal kama: Ruoth Yesu nokawo makati e otienono mane ondhogee,
\v 24 kendo bangʼ kosegoyo erokamano nongʼingo, kowacho niya, \wj “Ma en ringra mochiw nikech un, timuru ma ka uparago.”\wj*
\v 25 Kamano bende bangʼ chiemo nokawo kikombe, mi owacho niya, \wj “Kikombeni en singruok manyien motim gi remba; timuru ma, kinde duto mumadhee, mondo uparago.”\wj*
\v 26 Nikech ka usiko uchamo makatini kendo umadho kikombeni, to unyiso tho mar Ruoth nyaka chop oduogi.
\p 
\v 27 Emomiyo ngʼama ochamo makatini kata ometho e kikombeni e yo ma ok owinjore, bura biro loyo kodoko jaketho kuom ringre Ruoth gi rembe.
\v 28 Ngʼato ka ngʼato nyaka nonre mokwongo, kapok ochamo makati kata ometho e kikombe.
\v 29 Nikech ngʼato angʼata mochiemo kendo ometho, ma ok odewo ni gin ringre Ruoth, kelo bura kuome owuon.
\v 30 Mano emomiyo ji mathoth kuomu ool kendo tuo; kendo moko kuomu osetho.
\v 31 To ka dine wanonre wawegi mokwongo, to bura ok doloyowa.
\v 32 To ka Ruoth ngʼadonwa bura to orieyowa mondo kik bura lowa kaachiel gi jopinyni.
\p 
\v 33 Kuom mano, jowetena, ka uchokoru kaachiel mondo uchiem, to ngʼato ka ngʼato mondo orit nyawadgi.
\v 34 To ka ngʼato odenyo, to ber mondo ochiem dala, mondo kik chokruok ma ubedogo kelnu kum.
\p Weche modongʼ anawachnu ka abiro.
\c 12
\s1 Mich mag Roho
\p 
\v 1 Jowetena, daher mondo ungʼe adiera kuom mich mag Roho mondo kik ubed maonge ngʼeyo.
\v 2 Ungʼeyo ni kane pod un jopiny, makia Nyasaye, to ne chalo nine oywau gi nyiseche manono ma ok wuo mi ulal.
\v 3 Omiyo, adwaro mondo ungʼe ni ngʼama Roho mar Nyasaye otelone ok nyal wacho niya, “Okwongʼ Yesu” to bende onge ngʼama nyalo wacho niya, “Yesu en Ruoth” ka ok Roho Maler ema otelone.
\p 
\v 4 Nitie mich mag Roho mopogore opogore, to Roho achiel ema chiwogi.
\v 5 Nitie tije mopogore opogore, to Ruoth achiel ema itiyone.
\v 6 Nitie yore mathoth mitiyogo tich Nyasaye, to Nyasaye achiel ema chiwone ngʼato ka ngʼato teko mar tiyogi.
\p 
\v 7 Roho nenore e ngima ngʼato ka ngʼato e yo mopogore opogore, mondo okel konyruok ni ji duto.
\v 8 Ngʼat moro Roho omiyo nyalo mar wuoyo gi rieko, ngʼat machielo Rohono omiyo tiend ngʼeyo weche matut.
\v 9 Ngʼato Rohono miyo yie, to ngʼat machielo omiyo mich mar chango ji;
\v 10 ngʼat moro omiyo teko mar timo honni, moro omiyo teko mar hulo weche moa kuom Nyasaye, moro omiyo rieko mar fwenyo ma lingʼ-lingʼ mag chunje mopogore opogore, moro omiyo nyalo mar wuoyo gi dhok mayore, eka ngʼat moro to omiyo mich mar loko dhok mayoreyore.
\v 11 Magi duto gin tich mar Roho achiel machalre, kendo ochiwogi ni ngʼato ka ngʼato kaka ohero.
\s1 Ringruok achiel gi fuonde mangʼeny
\p 
\v 12 Kata obedo ni ringre dhano en achiel, to en gi fuonde mathoth, to bende kata obedo ni en gi fuonde mathoth, pod en mana ringruok achiel. Ma e kaka Kristo bende chalo.
\v 13 Kamano bende e kaka wan duto, bed ni wan jo-Yahudi kata jo-Yunani, kata wasumbini, kata joma ni thuolo, nobatiswa kuom Roho achielnogo mi wadoko ringruok achiel, kendo osemiwa Roho achielno mondo wamodhi waduto.
\v 14 Nikech ringruok ok olos gi fuoni achiel, to olose gi fuonde mangʼeny.
\p 
\v 15 Ka dipo ni tielo nyalo wacho niya, “Kaka ok an lwedo, ok an achiel kuom fuonde ringruok,” to mano ok nyal mone bedo achiel kuom fuonde ringruok.
\v 16 Kata, ka it nyalo wacho niya, “Kaka ok an wangʼ, ok an achiel kuom fuonde ringruok,” to mano ok nyal mone bedo achiel kuom fuonde ringruok.
\v 17 Ka dine bed ni ringruok duto en mana wangʼ kende, dowinj wach nadi? Kata ka dine ringruok duto bed mana it kende, ere kaka dongʼwe gik moko?
\v 18 To kata kamano, Nyasaye noketo fuoni ka fuoni e ringruok mana kaka ne odwaro ni mondo gibedi.
\v 19 Kane bed ni gin fuon achiel, to ringruok dibed nadi?
\v 20 E kaka obedo ni nitie fuonde mangʼeny, to ringruok en achiel.
\p 
\v 21 Kuom mano wangʼ ok nyal wachone lwedo niya, “Ok adwari!” Kata wich bende ok nyal wachone tielo niya, “Ok adwari.”
\v 22 To en adier ni ok wanyal bedo maonge gi fuonde ringruok manenorenwa ni nyap.
\v 23 Fuonde matindo wamiyo rit mamalo moloyo, kendo fuonde ma wakawo ni richo warwako maber moloyo.
\v 24 Fuonde mabeyo moloyo, to ok dwar rit ma kamano. Nyasaye owuon oseriwo fuonde mopogore opogore moloso ringruok, kendo osemiyo fuonde mwachayo duongʼ,
\v 25 mondo kik winjruok bed maonge e ringruok; to mondo fuon ka fuon orit nyawadgi kaka dwarore.
\v 26 Ka fuon achiel mar ringruok winjo lit, to fuonde ringruok mamoko duto winjo kode; ka fuon moro yudo pak, to mamoko duto bende bedo mamor kaachiel kode.
\p 
\v 27 E kaka un duto un ringre Kristo, kendo ngʼato ka ngʼato kuomu en fuon mar ringruogno.
\v 28 To ei kanisa, Nyasaye oseketo ji man-gi mich mopogore opogore e tichne: Mokwongo, joote, mar ariyo, jonabi, to mar adek, jopuonj, eka joma timo honni, kaeto joma omi teko mar chango joma tuo, kod jokony ji, kod joma otelo ni ji, to mogik, joma wuoyo gi dhok mayoreyore.
\v 29 Bende ji duto gin joote? Bende ji duto gin jonabi? Bende ji duto gin jopuonj? Bende ji duto timo honni?
\v 30 Bende ji duto nigi mich mar chango joma tuo? Bende ji duto wuoyo gi dhok mayoreyore? Bende ji duto nyalo loko tiend weche joma wuoyo gi dhok mayoreyore?
\v 31 Owinjore uket chunyu kuom mich madongo.
\p Koro abiro nyisou yo moro maber moloyo.
\c 13
\s1 Hera
\p 
\v 1 Kata bed ni awuoyo gi dhok mopogore opogore mag dhano kod mag malaike, to aonge gihera, to achalo mana ongengʼo maywak kata olangʼ migoyo.
\v 2 Ka an gi mich mar koro wach, kendo ka angʼeyo tiend weche matek duto modhiero ji ngʼeyo, kendo an gi rieko duto, kata ka an gi yie maduongʼ manyalo golo gode kuonde ma gintie, to ka aonge gihera; to ok an gimoro.
\v 3 Kata bed ni achiwo giga duto ma an-go ne jodhier, mi achiw ringra mondo owangʼ, to ka aonge gihera, to onge ohala mayudo.
\p 
\v 4 Hera timo kinda, kendo ongʼwon, oonge nyiego, ok osungre, bende ok opakre.
\v 5 Wiye ok tek, ok odwar mare kende, iye ok wangʼ piyo kendo ok omak sadha.
\v 6 Hera ok mor gi gik maricho, to omor gi adiera.
\v 7 Hera umo weche duto, osiko oyie ayieya, osiko ogeno agena, kendo osiko odhil adhila.
\p 
\v 8 Hera ok rum. To kama nitiere weche mikoro, weche mikoro norum; kama nitiere wuoyo gi dhok mayoreyore, dhok mayoreyore norum; kama nitiere ngʼeyo; ngʼeyo bende nokadhi.
\v 9 E thuoloni weche mwangʼeyo tin, to bende wakoro bath wach, ma mago mabiro chopo kare tin,
\v 10 to ka weche duto nochop kare, to mago morem nogiki.
\v 11 Kane an nyathi, ne awuoyo ka nyathi, ne aparo ka nyathi, kendo naneno ka nyathi, to koro kaka an ngʼama osebedo maduongʼ, yore mag nyithindo aseweyo chien.
\v 12 Gima waneno sani chal mana gi kido matip-tip mineno e rangʼi, to chiengʼno wananene wangʼ gi wangʼ. Gima angʼeyo sani en mana bath adiera, to chiengʼno anangʼe Nyasaye malongʼo chuth, mana kaka en bende ongʼeya.
\p 
\v 13 To nitie gik moko adek mosiko, ma gin: yie, geno, kod hera, to maduongʼ moloyo kuomgi en hera.
\c 14
\s1 Mich mag koro wach kod wuoyo gi dhok mayoreyore
\p 
\v 1 Luwuru hera, kendo dwaruru mondo ubed gi mich mag chuny, to moloyo beduru johul wach.
\v 2 Nikech ngʼat ma wuoyo gi dhok mayoreyore ok wuo gi ji, to owuoyo gi Nyasaye, nikech onge ngʼama winjo tiend gima owacho. Owacho weche mopondo modhiero ngʼeyo gi teko mar Roho.
\v 3 To ngʼat ma hulo wach, wuoyo gi ji mondo ogergi, ojiwgi kendo oduog chunygi.
\v 4 Ngʼat ma wuoyo gi dhok mayoreyore gerore kende owuon, to ngʼat ma hulo wach moa kuom Nyasaye gero kanisa.
\v 5 Daher mondo uwuo gi dhok mayoreyore uduto, to moloyo mano, ni mondo uhul wach. Ngʼat ma hulo wach duongʼ moloyo ngʼat ma wuoyo gi dhok mayoreyore makmana ka nitie ngʼat manyalo loko tiend wach modhumono, mondo kanisni duto oyud konyruok.
\p 
\v 6 Koro, jowetena, uparo ni ka abiro iru mi awuoyonu gi dhok mayoreyore, en konyruok mane ma duyudi, ka ok akelonu fweny moro kata ngʼeyo, kata wach mihulo kata puonj?
\v 7 Kata mana gik maonge ngima kuomgi, kaka asili, kata nyatiti, to dingʼe ywakgi nadi ka ok ipogo dwondgi?
\v 8 To bende, ka turumbete ok ogo gi dwol mongʼere, ngʼama diikre ni lweny?
\v 9 Chal kamano kuomu un bende. Ka ok ukonyoru gi weche maliw ma ji duto winjo, to ngʼama biro ngʼeyo tiend gima uwacho? Wecheu biro lal nono mana ka yamo!
\v 10 Ongʼere ni nitiere dhok mopogore opogore e piny, to onge kata achiel kuomgi maonge gi tiendgi.
\v 11 To ka ok apogo dwond ngʼato, to achalone jamwa, kendo en bende ochalona jamwa.
\v 12 Emomiyo un bende kaka udwaro mondo ubed gi mich mag Roho, temuru matek moloyo mondo unwangʼ mich mago magero kanisa.
\p 
\v 13 Kuom mano, ngʼat ma wuoyo gi dhok moro amora ma ji kia, olem mondo obed gi nyalo mar loko tiend gik mowacho.
\v 14 Nikech ka alamo gi dhok mayoreyore, to chunya ema alamogo, to pacha ok ti.
\v 15 To koro kara atim angʼo? Abiro lamo gi chunya, to bende abiro lamo gi pacha, abiro wer gi chunya, to bende abiro wer gi pacha.
\v 16 Ka upako Nyasaye gi chunyu, to ere kaka ngʼato manie dieru ma ok winji dhougo digo niya, “Amin” bangʼ erokamano mugoyo, ka okia gima uwacho?
\v 17 Nyalo bet ni igoyo erokamano maber chuth, to ngʼat machielo ok gerre.
\p 
\v 18 Adwokone Nyasaye erokamano nikech awuoyo gi dhok mayoreyore moloyo un duto,
\v 19 to ka an e kind kanisa, to daher wacho weche kata abich kende gi dhok ma ji duto winjo mondo apuonj moloyo weche alufu apar gi dhok mayoreyore ma ji ok winji.
\p 
\v 20 Jowetena, kik ubed nyithindo e pachu, to chaluru nyithindo mayom mana kuom gima rach kende, to e pachu beduru jomadongo.
\v 21 Ondiki e kitap chik niya,
\q1 “Anakonyra gi joma wacho dhok mayoreyore
\q2 kendo gi dho joma welo,
\q1 abiro wuoyo gi jogi
\q2 to kata kamano ok giniwinja,
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema wacho kamano.”\f + \fr 14:21 \ft \xt Isa 28:11,12\xt*\f*
\p 
\v 22 Kuom mano, mich mar wuoyo gi dhok mayoreyore en ranyisi miywayogo joma pok oyie, to ok joma oseyie. Mich mar hulo wach to en mar joma oseyie ok joma pok oyie.
\v 23 Omiyo ka kanisa ochokore kaachiel, to ji duto wuoyo gi dhok mayoreyore, to ka nitie jomoko ma ok winj dhogino, kata ka joma ok oyie moko odonjo e chokruogno, donge digiwach ni wiu okethore?
\v 24 To ka ngʼat ma ok oyie, kata ngʼat moro ma ok winj tiend gik miwacho odonjo e chokruoku, to oyudo ka ji duto hulo wach, weche mowinjo nyalo loye gi bura, mi olokre,
\v 25 kendo paro malingʼ-lingʼ mopondo e chunye elore e lela, mi opodh auma kolamo Nyasaye, kowacho niya, “Adier, Nyasaye ni kodu!”
\s1 Chenro mar lemo
\p 
\v 26 Jowetena, koro wanyalo wacho angʼo? Ka un e chokruok mar lemo, to yudore ni ngʼat moro nigi wer, to ngʼat machielo nigi puonj, to moro nigi fweny, to machielo dwaro wuoyo gi dhok mayoreyore kata loko tiend wach miwachono. To gigi duto nyaka tim e yo mochanore magero kanisa.
\v 27 Ka nitie joma wuoyo gi dhok mayoreyore, to ji ariyo kata adek ka ngʼeny kende ema mondo owuo, to mana e yo mochanore maber, ka moro ka moro wuoyo bangʼ wadgi, kendo ngʼato nyaka lok tiend weche ma giwachogo.
\v 28 To kaonge ngʼato manyalo loko tiend wechego, to ngʼat ma wuoyo gi dhok mayoreyore mondo olingʼ e kanisa, to owuo mana e chunye owuon kende gi Nyasaye.
\p 
\v 29 Joma hulo wach kik bed mokalo ji ariyo kata adek, kendo ka giwuoyo, to ji mamoko onon mos ka bende weche magiwacho owinjore.
\v 30 To ka ngʼato moro manie chokruokno omi wach moro mopondo mondo owachi, ngʼat mane oyudo dhi nyime gi wuoyo nyaka lingʼ mondi, eka owuo.
\v 31 Nikech un duto unyalo hulo wach, ka ngʼato ka ngʼato koro bangʼ nyawadgi, mondo ji duto oyud puonj kod jip.
\v 32 Roho mar janabi niginyalo mar gengʼo wach ma odwaro wacho,
\v 33 nikech Nyasaye ok en Nyasach koko, to en Nyasach kwe.
\p To mana kaka timore ei kanisa mar jomaler,
\v 34 jomamon onego olingʼ e kanisa. Ok oyienigi wuoyo, nyaka giwinj puonj mana ka gilingʼ kaka chik wacho.
\v 35 Ka gidwaro mondo olernigi tiend wach moro, to gipenj chwogi giwegi dala, nikech en wichkuot ka dhako wuoyo e kanisa.
\p 
\v 36 Koro kuparo ni un ema ne wach Nyasaye ochakore kuomu? Koso ugalo ni un kendu ema wach osechoponu?
\v 37 Ka ngʼato okawore ni en jahul wach kata ni en gi mich mar Roho, to nyaka oyie ni wach mandikonuni en chik Ruoth.
\v 38 Ka ngʼato ok orwako puonjnani, to en bende ok norwake.
\p 
\v 39 Kuom mano, jowetena, gomburu bedo johul wach, to kik utam ji wuoyo gi dhok mayoreyore.
\v 40 Timuru gik moko duto e yo mowinjore kendo mochanore.
\c 15
\s1 Chier mar Kristo
\p 
\v 1 Koro jowetena, adwaro paronu wach Injili mane ayalonu, mi urwako kendo koro uchungoe motegno.
\v 2 Injilini ema kelonu warruok, ka umako matek wach mane ayalonu mokwongo. Ka ok kamano, to kara ne uyie kayiem nono.
\p 
\v 3 Puonj maduongʼ mogik mane ayudo kuom Ruoth mi amiyou ema: Kristo notho nikech richowa kaluwore gi Ndiko,
\v 4 kendo ne oike, bangʼe ochiere oa kuom joma otho chiengʼ mar adek kaluwore gi Ndiko,
\v 5 kendo ne ofwenyore mokwongo ne Petro, bangʼe nofwenyore ne joote apar gariyo.
\v 6 Bangʼ mano nofwenyore ni jowete moloyo mia abich, ka gin kanyachiel, kendo thothgi pod ngima nyaka sani, kata obedo ni moko kuomgi osetho.
\v 7 Achien nofwenyore ne Jakobo; bangʼe nofwenyore ne joote duto,
\v 8 eka achien mogik, ne ofwenyorena apoya an bende, mana ka nyathi mobwogi.
\p 
\v 9 An e jaote matinie mogik, to bende ok awinjora mondo oluonga ni jaote, nikech ne asando kanisa Nyasaye.
\v 10 To koro, kuom ngʼwono mar Nyasaye, an gima an, kendo ngʼwono mane omiya ne ok orem mak ochopo tichne. Chutho, asetiyo matek moloyo joote mamoko duto, to ok asetimo mago duto gi tekra awuon, to mana kuom ngʼwono mar Nyasaye ma an-go.
\v 11 Omiyo kata bed ni an ema ne ayalonu Injili kata gin ema ne giyalonu, to ma e gima waduto wayalo kendo ema ne uyie.
\s1 Chier mar joma otho kuom Kristo
\p 
\v 12 To ka iyalo ni Kristo osechier oa kuom joma otho, to angʼo momiyo jomoko kuomu wacho ni joma otho ok bi chier?
\v 13 Ka en adier ni joma otho ok chier, to mano nyiso ni kata Kristo bende pok ochier?
\v 14 To ka Kristo pok ochier, to wayalo kayiem, kendo yie maru bende onge tiende.
\v 15 To moloyo mano, wadoko joneno mariambo kuom Nyasaye nikech wasebedo ka wanyiso ji ni Nyasaye ema ne osechiero Kristo oa kuom joma otho. To kara ne ok ochiere ka en adier ni joma otho ok chier?
\v 16 Nikech ka joma otho ok chier, to kata Kristo bende pok ochier.
\v 17 To ka Kristo pok ochier, to yie maru en nono; kendo pod ulal alala e richou.
\v 18 Mano nyiso bende ni jo-Kristo mosetho bende olal.
\v 19 Ka genowa kuom Kristo nigi tiende mana e ngimani kende, to kare wan joma odhierie moloyo ji duto.
\p 
\v 20 To adiera en ni Kristo osechier oa kuom joma otho. Chierneno en kaka gir singo manyiso ni joma osetho e liel bende ibiro chiero.
\v 21 Nikech kaka tho noa kuom ngʼat achiel e kaka chier mar joma otho bende osebiro koa kuom ngʼat achiel.
\v 22 Mana kaka ji duto tho nikech Adam, e kaka ji duto nobed mangima nikech Kristo.
\v 23 To gigi nyaka timre e yo mochanore: Kristo mane okwongo chier kaka olemo mokwongo chiek, eka bangʼe joma ni kuome bende nochier chiengʼ manoduogi.
\v 24 Bangʼ mano, giko nochopi, mi Kristo nolo joloch duto, nolo teko duto kendo nolo nyalo duto, eka nodwok pinyruoth ni Nyasaye Wuoro,
\v 25 nimar Kristo nyaka bed gi loch nyaka chop Nyasaye lo wasigu duto, mi oketgi e bwo tiende.
\v 26 Jasigu manotieki achien mogik en tho,
\v 27 nikech ndiko wacho niya, “oseketo gik moko duto e bwo tiende.”\f + \fr 15:27 \ft \xt Zab 8:6\xt*\f* To ka ndiko wuoyo kuom “gik moko duto” to ongʼere ni mano ok oriwo Nyasaye owuon nikech en ema oketo gik moko duto e bwo loch Kristo.
\v 28 To ka gik moko duto oseketi e bwo loch Kristo, bangʼe en bende enobed e bwo loch Nyasaye, mane oketo gik moko duto e bwoye, mondo Nyasaye obed gi loch ewi gik moko duto.
\p 
\v 29 To kapo ni chier onge, to ere tiende batiso ji ewi joma osetho? Ka joma otho ok chier, to ibatiso ji e wigi nangʼo?
\v 30 To kata mana wan, angʼo ma dimi wachom masira seche duto?
\v 31 Jowetena, kaka un e sungana kuom Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo awachonu ka aramo, ni tho ochoma pile!
\v 32 Ka dipo ni ne akedo gi le makwiny e dala Efeso mana nikech dwach dhano to ohala mane ma ayudo? Ka joma otho ok chier,
\q1 to we wachiem kendo wamethi,
\q2 nikech kiny wanatho.\f + \fr 15:32 \ft \xt Isa 22:13\xt*\f*
\m 
\v 33 Kik ngʼato wuondu. Ngʼeuru niya, “Bedo e lalruok kod joma richo ketho timbe mabeyo.”
\v 34 Dwoguru e pachu maliw, daguru ngima makare kendo weuru timo richo, nikech nitie jomoko kuomu makia Nyasaye. Awacho kamano mondo akuodgo wiu.
\s1 Chier mar ringruok
\p 
\v 35 To ngʼato nyalo penjo niya, “Joma otho ichiero nadi? To jogi nobed gi ringruok machalo nade?”
\v 36 To mano penjo mofuwo manade! Ka uchwoyo kodhi, to nyaka okuong otho eka bangʼe otwi.
\v 37 Ka uchwoyo, to ok en cham hie mabiro wuok bangʼe, to en mana kodhi kende. Onyalo bedo koth ngano kata koth cham moro amora.
\v 38 To Nyasaye miye kido mana kaka en ema osechano, kendo kodhi ka kodhi omiyo kite owuon.
\v 39 Ringruok duto ok chalre. Dhano nigi kit ringruok moro, to le nigi machielo, winy bende nigi machielo, kendo rech bende nigi machielo.
\v 40 Nitie bende chwech mag polo gi chwech mag piny, kendo kit duongʼ mar chwech mag polo opogore gi kit duongʼ mar chwech mag piny.
\v 41 Wangʼ chiengʼ nigi kit ler ma mare owuon, to dwe bende nigi machielo, kendo sulwe bende nigi mare. Sulwe ka sulwe chiwo ler mopogore gi nyawadgi.
\p 
\v 42 Kamano bende e kaka chier mar joma otho biro chalo. Ringruok ma iyiko en gima tow, to ichiere ka en gima ok tow.
\v 43 Ka oike, to oonge gi duongʼ, to ichiere ka en gi duongʼ, to bende iyike ka onyap, to ichiere ka en gi teko,
\v 44 kendo iyike kaka ringruok mar pinyni, to ichiere kaka ringruok mar polo.
\p Ka nitiere ringruok mar piny, to nitiere bende ringruok mar polo.
\v 45 Emomiyo ondiki niya, “Adam ma en dhano mokwongo, nobedo ngʼat mangima”\f + \fr 15:45 \ft \xt Chak 2:7\xt*\f* to Adam mogik nodoko chuny machiwo ngima.
\v 46 To mano mar Roho ok ema kuongi, to mar ringruok ema kuongo, eka bangʼe mar Roho.
\v 47 Dhano mokwongo nochwe gi lowo, to dhano mar ariyo noa e polo.
\v 48 Ngʼat mane ochwe gi lowo ema ji duto oa kuome, kamano bende e kaka jopolo duto oa kuom Jal mane oa e polo.
\v 49 Mana kaka wasebedo gi kido mar dhano mochwe gi lowo, e kaka wabiro chalo gi kido mar dhano moa e polo.
\p 
\v 50 Jowetena, tiend gima awacho ema: Ringruok gi remo ok nyal chamo girkeni mar pinyruodh Nyasaye kendo gima tow ok nyal rwakore gi gima ok tow.
\v 51 Winjuru anena wach mopondoni: Ok wanatho waduto, to nolokwa wan duto apoya nono
\v 52 kadiemo wangʼ ka tungʼ mogik noywagi. Nikech ka turumbete noywagi to jomane osetho nochier gi ringruok ma ok tow, to wan to nolokwa ahucha.
\v 53 Mano notimre nikech ringruok matow nyaka rwakre gi ringruok ma ok tow, kendo ringruok mathoni nyaka rwakre gi ringruok ma ok tho.
\v 54 Kuom mano, ka ringruok matow oserwakore gi mano ma ok tow, kendo mano matho oserwakore gi mano ma ok tho, eka wach mondiki nochop kare, niya, “Tho oselo motiek chuth.”\f + \fr 15:54 \ft \xt Isa 25:8\xt*\f*
\q1 
\v 55 In tho, koro ere lochni?
\q2 In tho, lit mikelo ni kanye?\f + \fr 15:55 \ft \xt Hos 13:14\xt*\f*
\m 
\v 56 Lit mar tho en richo, to teko mar richo en chik.
\v 57 To erokamano ni Nyasaye. Omiyowa loch kuom Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo!
\p 
\v 58 Emomiyo, jowetena mageno, chunguru motegno. Kik uyie gimoro oyiengu. Chiwreuru chuth kinde duto ni tich Ruoth, nikech ungʼeyo ni tich mutiyo matek ne Ruoth ok obedo kayiem nono.
\c 16
\s1 Chiwo michoko ne jo-Nyasaye
\p 
\v 1 To koro kuom wach choko chiwo ni jo-Nyasaye; to awachoe kama: Timuru gima ne akone kanisa man Galatia mondo otim.
\v 2 Odiechiengʼ mokwongo mar juma ngʼato ka ngʼato kuomu nyaka pog mich moko tenge, kaluwore gi yuto mare mondo ka abiro to onge mich mibiro chok kendo.
\v 3 Yieruru jomoko kuomu mondo ka biro to andiknegi barupe mapwodhogigo mondo giter mich muchokogo Jerusalem.
\v 4 Ka ber mondo an bende adhi, to ginidhi koda.
\s1 Kwayo mag Paulo owuon
\p 
\v 5 Abiro biro iru bangʼ ka asea Makedonia, nikech abiro luwo kuno.
\v 6 Sa moro anyalo bedo kodu kuom ndalo mogwarore, to sa moro anyalo bedo kodu mana e ndalo mag chwiri kende mondo omi ukonya e wuodhena duto mabiro dhiyoe.
\v 7 Ok adwar mondo anenu mana ayuka ka akadho, to ageno mar bedo kodu amingʼa, ka Ruoth oyie.
\v 8 To pod abiro dak Efeso-ka nyaka chiengʼ Pentekost,
\v 9 nikech dhoot oyaworena malach mar tiyo tich manyago olemo, to wasigu makedo koda bende ngʼeny.
\p 
\v 10 Ka Timotheo obiro iru, neuru ni obedo kodu kaonge gima oluoro, nikech otiyo ni Ruoth, mana kaka an.
\v 11 Kuom mano, kik ngʼato angʼata otamre ma ok orwake, to konyeuru mondo odhi nyime e wuodhe gi kwe, mondo oyud yo mar duogo ira nikech arite en kaachiel gi jowete mamoko.
\p 
\v 12 To kuom wach owadwa Apolo, to awacho kama: Ne ajiwe matek mondo olimu kod jowete mamoko, to pok oyie chuth ni onego obi iru sani, to ka oyudo thuolo, to obiro biro achien.
\p 
\v 13 Beduru motangʼ, kendo chunguru motegno e yie maru, bende beduru jochir kendo motegno.
\v 14 Timuru gik moko duto gihera.
\p 
\v 15 Ungʼeyo ni jood Stefano e joma nokwongo yie kuom Kristo e piny Akaya, kendo gisechiwore mar tiyo ni jo-Nyasaye. Ajiwou, jowetena,
\v 16 mondo uyie bet e bwo joma kamago, kendo e bwo joma tiyo kaachiel kodgi.
\v 17 Ne adoko mamor kane Stefano gi Fortunato kod Akaiko ne obiro ira, nikech ne gichopona gima ne aremo mane onego un uwegi umiya.
\v 18 Negidwogo chunya, kaachiel kod un bende. Joma kamago onego omi duongʼ.
\b
\s1 Mos mogik
\p 
\v 19 Kanyakla mar joma oyie kuom Kristo man Asia ooronu mos.
\p Akula gi Priskila, kaachiel gi kanisa machokore e odgi, ooronu mos gi mor kuom Ruoth.
\p 
\v 20 Jowete duto man ka ooronu mos.
\p Yogreuru ngʼato gi ngʼato gi mos maler.
\b
\p 
\v 21 An Paulo awuon ema andikonu mosni gi lweta awuon.
\b
\p 
\v 22 Ka ngʼato ok ohero Ruoth, to mondo okwongʼe! Yaye Ruoth, bi.
\b
\p 
\v 23 Ngʼwono mar Ruoth Yesu obed kodu.
\b
\p 
\v 24 Herana obed kodu un duto ei Kristo Yesu. Amin.
